state_description: Initial state after navigation: how can i find my most recently created page in notion
llm_enhanced_instruction: Navigate to the Notion homepage by entering 'https://www.notion.so/' in your web browser's address bar to access your workspace and find your most recently created page.
llm_context: You should see the Notion homepage with a list of your recent pages displayed prominently in the center, indicating that you're ready to locate your latest work.
